				<p class="mt-3 text-base font-serif text-gray-600">裏面は、情報量が多かったですが特に伝えたい情報を大きくし、全体を優しい緑でまとめました。</p>
			</div>
		</div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row mt-12">
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
			<div class="w-full font-bold text-gray-600 md:w-1/8">公開時期</div>
			<div class="w-full font-serif text-gray-600 md:w-5/8">2025.05</div>
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
		</div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row mt-3">
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
			<div class="w-full font-bold text-gray-600 md:w-1/8">制作期間</div>
			<div class="w-full font-serif text-gray-600 md:w-5/8">2週間程度</div>
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
		</div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row mt-3">
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
			<div class="w-full font-bold text-gray-600 md:w-1/8">クライアント</div>
			<div class="w-full font-serif text-gray-600 md:w-5/8">LOYLOY</div>
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
		</div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row mt-3">
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
			<div class="w-full font-bold text-gray-600 md:w-1/8">使用技術</div>
			<div class="w-full font-serif text-gray-600 md:w-5/8">
                <p>Photoshop /Illustrator</p>
            </div>
			<div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/8"></div>
		</div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row mt-3 pb-12">
